This message reports the status of internal and external oscillators and sources as well aswhether GNSS is used for disciplining.

column7: A bit mask, indicating the status of the localoscillator (see graphic below)
A bit mask, indicating the status of the externaloscillator (see graphic below)
Disciplining source identifier:0: internal oscillator1: GNSS2: EXTINT03: EXTINT14: internal oscillator measured by the host5: external oscillator measured by the host
A bit mask, indicating the status of the GNSS(see graphic below)
A bit mask, indicating the status of the externalinput 0 (see graphic below)
A bit mask, indicating the status of the externalinput 1 (see graphic below)
